the hypoxic environments is

100
00:06:19,610 --> 00:06:21,270
critical to such advancements.

101
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:26,310
And finally, because hypoxia is a whole
body stressor,

102
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:30,260
it helps us understand the integration of
the whole body systems.

103
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:33,930
We apply a stress to the system, see how
it responds, and

104
00:06:33,930 --> 00:06:37,040
it gives us a stronger understanding of
basic physiology.

105
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:43,700
